OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781218983
OL,3,CHarry Maguire and Manchester United
OL,4,Cteammates fined for speeding
OL,6,FManchester United player Harry Maguire
OL,7,Fhas been handed a #1,000 fine as two
OL,8,Fother teammates are also prosecuted
OL,9,Ffor speeding.
OL,11,FThe 33-year-old centre-back, who was
OL,12,Frecently left out of Thomas Tuchel's
OL,13,F26-man England World Cup squad, was
OL,14,Fcaught driving his #130,000 Range
OL,15,FRover at 37mph in a 30mph zone in
OL,16,FAltrincham, Greater Manchester.
OL,18,FThe offence happened in December 2025,
OL,19,Fas he travelled between Old Trafford
OL,20,Fand his Cheshire home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
