FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781218983
OL,3,CHarry Maguire and Manchester United
OL,4,Cteammates fined for speeding
OL,6,FThe former England regular, who
OL,7,Freceived a 56-day road ban in January
OL,8,F2025 for previous speeding offences,
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty in writing and was
OL,10,Fsentenced at Tameside Magistrates'
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FMaguire, who said he had been "left
OL,14,Fshocked and gutted" at being left out
OL,15,Fof the England Squad, also received
OL,16,Fthree penalty points, and must pay
OL,17,F#120 in costs and a #400 victim
OL,18,Fsurcharge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781218983
OL,3,CHarry Maguire and Manchester United
OL,4,Cteammates fined for speeding
OL,6,FMaguire apologised to the court and
OL,7,Fsaid "I was driving at 37mph in what I
OL,8,Fmistakenly believed was a 40mph zone,
OL,9,Fwhen it was in fact a 30mph limit.
OL,11,F"I understand this was my
OL,12,Fresponsibility and I fully accept the
OL,13,Foffence. I will be more careful in
OL,14,Ffuture and pay closer attention to
OL,15,Fspeed limit signs."
OL,26,@oD@FOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
