OL,3,CHarry Maguire and Manchester United
OL,4,Cteammates fined for speeding
OL,6,FAt the same time, United reserve
OL,7,Fgoalkeeper 28-year-old Altay Bayindir
OL,8,Fwas also fined after admitting to
OL,9,Fdriving a Mercedes at 41mph in a 30mph
OL,10,Flimit in Hale Barns, shortly after a
OL,11,FPremier League defeat to Everton.
OL,13,FBayindir, who has been called up for
OL,14,FTurkey's World Cup campaign, was fined
OL,15,F#666 with three penalty points, #120
OL,16,Fcosts and a #266 victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781218983
OL,3,CHarry Maguire and Manchester United
OL,4,Cteammates fined for speeding
OL,6,FThe third Manchester United star to
OL,7,Ffind himself in legal difficulties is
OL,8,FMatheus Cunha, who has been charged
OL,9,Fwith speeding and failing to respond
OL,10,Fto police letters asking him to
OL,11,Fidentify the driver of the vehicle.
OL,13,FCourt papers showed the Mercedes was
OL,14,Fregistered in the name of the
OL,15,FBrazilian striker and was clocked at
OL,16,F37mph, on the same stretch of Hale
OL,17,FRoad where Bayindir was caught
OL,18,Fspeeding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781218983
OL,3,CHarry Maguire and Manchester United
OL,4,Cteammates fined for speeding
OL,6,FThe offence is alleged to have
OL,7,Fhappened following United's opening-
OL,8,Fday defeat to Arsenal.
OL,10,FCunha, who is part of Brazil's World
OL,11,FCup squad, has yet to enter a plea and
OL,12,Fwill be required to attend a hearing
OL,13,Fin December, where disqualification
OL,14,Ffrom driving will be considered at
OL,15,FBolton Magistrates' Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
